# Privacy — <%= appName %>

Subject-access export, erasure, consent, cookie tracking, and processing records.

## Layout

```
src/privacy/
  consent/
  cookies/
  processing/
  export/
  deletion/
tests/privacy/
PRIVACY.md
```

## CLI

```bash
my privacy export --user user-1
my privacy delete --user user-1
```

## Usage

```ts
import {
  privacyService,
  privacyUserStore,
  dataExporter,
  dataDeleter,
} from './src/privacy/index.js';

privacyUserStore.setProfile('user-1', { email: 'a@b.com' });
await privacyService.consentService.grant('user-1', 'marketing');
await privacyService.cookies.track('analytics', '_ga', 'set', { userId: 'user-1' });
await privacyService.processing.record('user-1', 'account', 'contract', ['email']);

const dump = await dataExporter.export('user-1');
const erased = await dataDeleter.delete('user-1');
```

## Features

- Export user data
- Delete user data
- Consent management
- Cookie tracking
- Data processing records
